 person some villagers had ever seen  heller zoë october   the haunted mind of shirley jackson the new yorker retrieved february     franklin ruth  shirley jackson a rather haunted life liveright isbn   accessdate requires url help  a b c shirley jackson contemporary authors online detroit gale  retrieved via biography in context database  the haunting of hill house has become one of the most respected haunted house stories  a b shirley hardie jackson dictionary of american biography new york charles scribners sons  retrieved via biography in context database   missing sophie february   review of the haunting of hill house by shirley jackson the guardian retrieved  the haunting of hill house  is a chilling and highly accomplished piece of writing justly described by stephen king as one of the most important horror novels of the th century  shirley jackson papers library of congress retrieved    powers tim december   remember paula welden  years ago bennington banner   ruth franklin may   shirley jackson’s ‘life among the savages’ and ‘raising demons’ reissued the new york times retrieved february     hyman stanley edgar  preface from the first edition  in shirley jackson come along with me classic short stories and an unfinished novel new york penguin isbn   shirley jacksons the lottery potrzebieblogspotcom retrieved    kates joan giangrasse  james a miller  independent gaffer lit movies for major players chicago tribune   we have always lived in the castle retrieved    cressida leyshon july   this week in fiction shirley jackson the new yorker retrieved    joshi s t june   shirley jackson domestic horror the modern weird tale a critique of horror fiction mcfarland  co isbn    haines colin december   frightened by a word shirley jackson  lesbian gothic studia anglistica upsaliensia uppsala universitet isbn    elaine showalter september   shirley jackson a rather haunted life the washington post retrieved february     robin finn july   public lives the mostly late gr